先出黎討論啦........"},{"pid":"ee72edfc71a3e2f9fb24e674385039f563c03ee5","tid":195241,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8ed556099ae745d4b3000212baa4d58c7ca0e667","tid":195241,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府想條廢鐵壟斷晒成個交通</blockquote><br />\n其實好多大城市都係咁，鐵路一死實仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港交通問題係地埋問題, 去過人地D觀光塔就知人地市中心就真係市中心. 香港先係南面仲要隔過海.<br />\n<br />\n香港應該另設兩個新市心. 一來可以大增商廈面積, 二來分擔交通過度集中問題."},{"pid":"6ddd7f813515d5b2cb6555c66c35cbd4dfd47319","tid":195241,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人真係試過去信諮詢嗰啲？<br />\n我覺得以上d idea都幾好</blockquote><br />\nIdea呢啲有咗幾耐, 點砌埋點實行先得㗎, 有份量嘅人出馬都動搖唔到"},{"pid":"87c1ffbf0c69d09ff558d1e98fde59eba858e4ab","tid":195241,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4339ab08440fb0b40433ef395b271952b933cc6c","tid":195241,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"你當地鐵等於 windows<br />\nwindows 成日中毒 d 人都係屌住用<br />\n就知 d 人即使地鐵日日故障都係屌住搭"},{"pid":"65391ca881bdf6799eae8df3b49a46d4759ffdab","tid":195241,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直覺得私家車好大問題<br />\n朝早驟眼睇條路7成都私家車<br />\n塞撚住哂 你三架就等於一架巴士<br />\n坐滿12人vs百幾人<br />\n啲人塞車咪衝去地鐵囉 唔想遲到嘛</blockquote><br />\n屌 咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明香港都撚細 都咁多人渣車"},{"pid":"26d26f9d3b837739006a3d3fd17d400e9ed76fa8","tid":195241,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政府想條廢鐵壟斷晒成個交通</blockquote><br />\n其實好多大城市都係咁，鐵路一死實仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港交通問題係地埋問題, 去過人地D觀光塔就知人地市中心就真係市中心. 香港先係南面仲要隔過海.<br />\n<br />\n香港應該另設兩個新市心. 一來可以大增商廈面積, 二來分擔交通過度集中問題.</blockquote><br />\n而家話九東同埋北大嶼山啊麻<br />\n唔撚知搞幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n*東大嶼 <br />\n北大嶼山英治美好玫瑰園"},{"pid":"81849abbe4167d88943c67fb59faee462a5617d3","tid":195241,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:06:22.000Z","msg":"中九龍幹線應該儘快起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131027d65ab5cdb8660305aec5ae0bd17766fa39","tid":195241,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趕撚走哂d死蝗蟲咪唔會overload囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歸鄉政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29f61e668fad45e3ba672c3dcd6bcbc610fbb53","tid":195241,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T20:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一直覺得私家車好大問題<br />\n朝早驟眼睇條路7成都私家車<br />\n塞撚住哂 你三架就等於一架巴士<br />\n坐滿12人vs百幾人<br />\n啲人塞車咪衝去地鐵囉 唔想遲到嘛</blockquote><br />\n屌 咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明香港都撚細 都咁多人渣車</blockquote><br />\n其實真係嬲 覺得啲人想攬炒<br />\n你係私家車塞 我係巴士塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府又唔撚做野 揸車既人就愈黎愈多<br />\n一係高空（起天橋）地下街又有咩水管屎渠<br />\n但天橋長途又做唔到 最後想快又係地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aacd7a3b340c9069e20bb51df1edcd1d219ea0a","tid":195241,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T20:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28b3e914afdc134eb94a3bda901f5e28ebd93969","tid":195241,"uid":16555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T21:20:51.000Z","msg":"其實重點得一個，就係人太多。即使交通政策勁到飛天，頂多都係舒緩，<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span>令交通情況變得完美。<br />\n當然，而家政府連舒緩交通苦況既能力都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"